## 8. Tableau Versions 💻  
Before exercises, here are the Tableau Desktop versions:

### 🆓 Tableau Desktop Public Edition
- Free version of Tableau  
- Most features included  
- Connects to:
  - Excel  
  - CSV files  
  - Google Sheets  
  - Some web data sources  
- 📦 Limited to 15 million rows  
- 💾 Save locally or publish online  

📌 Note: Since April 2024  

---

### 💼 Paid Tableau Desktop Version
- Requires a license  
- Same visualization features  
- 🔗 Connects to all data sources  
- 📊 Unlimited data rows  
- 💾 Save locally or online  

📌 Note: Since April 2024  

---

